WEBVTT

00:06:28.320 --> 00:06:30.480
I started opening strange doors.

00:06:32.480 --> 00:06:35.560
What if aliens came to Lagos, Nigeria?

00:06:38.800 --> 00:06:41.240
This is an excerpt
from my novel, "Lagoon."

00:06:44.320 --> 00:06:46.296
Everybody saw it,

00:06:46.320 --> 00:06:47.920
all over the world.

00:06:48.760 --> 00:06:52.296
That was a real introduction
to the great mess happening in Lagos,

00:06:52.320 --> 00:06:56.880
Nigeria, West Africa, Africa, here.

